145
00:14:10,210 --> 00:14:13,150
- I need to get home.
- [Gator] Nadine?

146
00:14:18,290 --> 00:14:19,920
Gator.

147
00:14:22,660 --> 00:14:24,160
Nadine.

148
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,300
